    "title": "Maharashtra Elections 2024: Complete list of winners in Mumbai, Suburban, and MMR",
    "text": "With the Mahayuti alliance inching closer to victory and likely to form the government in Maharashtra, here's the complete list of Maharashtra Elections 2024 winners in Mumbai, Mumbai Sururban and MMR region. (Pic/X, Instagram and Facebook)\nUpdated On: 2024-11-23 05:49 PM IST\nCompiled by : Joy Manikumar\nCongress leader Aslam Shaikh wins from Malad West\nMaharashtra Legislative Assembly speaker and BJP leader Rahul Narwekar wins from Colaba\nBJP leader Parag Shah wins from Ghatkopar (East) constituency\nEknath Shinde-led Shiv Sena leader Vilas Tare wins from Boisar constituency\nBJP leader Sulbha Gaikwad wins from Kalyan East constituency\nBJP leader Parag Alavani wins from Vile Parle constituency\nEight-time Member of Legislative Assembly (MLA) and BJP leader Kalidas Kolambkar wins from Wadala\nBJP leader Sneha Dubey Pandit wins from Vasai constituency\nShiv Sena (UBT) leader Haroon Khan wins from Versova constituency\nShiv Sena (UBT) leader Aaditya Thackeray retains his Worli seat\nEknath Shinde-led Shiv Sena leader Murji Patel wins from Andheri East constituency\nBJP leader Atul Bhatkhalkar wins from Kandivali East constituency\nMaharashtra CM Ekanth Shinde wins from Thane Kopri - Pachpakhadi constituency",
